			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"><span style="font-style: italic">She rolled over, gracefully raising out of the bed in one smooth movement. Without meeting his eyes, she gathered her clothing, and placed it on the corner of the bed, dressing slowly, unconcerned with her nudity, yet not wanting to prolong the intimacy. Gratis sighed softly. “You used to stay here with me. You used to lay in my arms all night.” 
<br />

<br />
Throwing her soft leather tunic over her head and tightening the straps, she shook her head. “That was a long time ago, I was a foolish child. I have things to do now, I will see you later Gratis.” The leggings slid on easily as well, the outfit tight, formfitting, and flattering, though with very little ornament. Its deep crimson color looked the color of blood against her milky white skin. 
<br />

<br />
“How many times do I have to apologize about leaving you back then? You are not as hard as you think you are.” He watched as she sat on the edge of the bed, pulling matching boots on and quickly lacing them up to her thighs to hold them in place. Her daggers went on last, slid smoothly into two sheaths at her hip, with another dagger concealed at the top of her boot, and a tiny but deadly sharp and poisoned one hanging in an ornate sheath attached to a chain around her neck, looking more like jewelry than the weapon it was. 
<br />

<br />
She walked silently to the door, then turned, looking at him with her eyes carefully void of all expression. “You are the one who is wrong, Gratis. I’m every bit as hard. You are the one who insists on seeing that simpering girl where she nau longer exists. Accept that she’s gone and take what I give you, or leave, and I can find another. Decide soon, jaluk, before I grow tired of this situation.”</span><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=738273" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v701/evileene/evilsig2.jpg" border="0" /></a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
